	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If its just a rusty power plug de-soldering the plug and putting a new one on will fix it, one that fits well enough in the NES can be found at radioshack. More exact replacements can be got online, I forget the exact size. You can try to remove the rust with sos, sandpaper or whatever you might get it going that way.

		

		</td>
