<br />
<br />I used the same AC adapter on this NES as with my working NES, so that rules out #1. It looks like if I could obtain a multimeter, I should try 2 and 3. Could you point me to a good online resource for the proper way to use a multimeter? What would I be looking for... "life?" or a specific voltage?

		

